snippet.title: Eggggg: Sticky puke and other fun stuff
snippet.description:
Soft launch, Norway only! 

"A videogame about puking shouldn't be this darn cute"
- Killscreen

Eggggg is a crazy platformer about Gilbert and his extreme egg allergy. Gilbert really wants to go to a birthday party, but his mean aunt Doris will not let him. After a daring escape he needs to use his vomiting superpower to survive a world of angry cyborg chickens.

By downloading you will get to experience
* A fun and playful game for all ages
* Smooth game controls – tailored for touch devices
* Awesome and unique characters and visual style by Brosmind
* Loads of puking
